        'Open /STR_02_Corporate_Plan.docx in Word for Web. Using Copilot in Word with /STR_05_KPI_Tree.xlsx as additional context, draft a FY2026 growth thesis refresh annex for the CEO covering the macro assumptions that have changed, the divisional growth trajectories that need revision, and the strategic bets that remain valid vs those requiring re-underwriting. Present as a structured table followed by a 200-word thesis statement the CEO can socialise with the Board. Use Edit with Copilot to align tone with the Group\'s formal strategic planning language.'
